dane_analysis.message: DANE not available — Google Workspace does not support inbound DANE/TLSA on its MX infrastructure

mx_provider.reason: Google Workspace supports DANE for outbound mail verification but does not publish TLSA records for its MX hosts.

dkim_analysis.message: DKIM not discoverable via common selectors (large providers use rotating selectors)

issues: No np= tag (DMARCbis) — non-existent subdomains inherit p= policy but adding np=reject provides explicit protection against subdomain spoofing

dnssec_analysis.message: DNSSEC not configured - DNS responses are unsigned

mta_sts_analysis.message: MTA-STS enforced - TLS required for 3 mail server(s)
mta_sts_analysis.policy:
version: STSv1
mode: enforce
mx: smtp.google.com
mx: aspmx.l.google.com
mx: *.aspmx.l.google.com
max_age: 86400

ns_delegation_analysis.note: Parent zone delegation could not be verified

posture.label: Email authentication with full DMARC enforcement. DNSSEC not configured.
posture.message: Email authentication with full DMARC enforcement. DNSSEC not configured.

verdicts.brand: Certificate issuance restricted via CAA. BIMI not configured for brand logo protection.
verdicts.dns: DNS responses are unsigned and could be spoofed. DNSSEC provides cryptographic verification.
verdicts.email: DMARC policy is reject — spoofed messages will be blocked by receiving servers. DKIM keys verified (provider-verified for Google Workspace).

all_fixes.fix: DNSSEC (DNS Security Extensions) cryptographically signs DNS responses, preventing attackers from forging DNS answers. Contact your DNS hosting provider to enable DNSSEC signing.
all_fixes.title: Enable DNSSEC

all_fixes.fix: Publish a BIMI DNS record pointing to your brand logo (SVG Tiny PS format). For full support in Gmail, you will also need a Verified Mark Certificate (VMC).
all_fixes.title: Configure BIMI brand logo

top_fixes.fix: DNSSEC (DNS Security Extensions) cryptographically signs DNS responses, preventing attackers from forging DNS answers. Contact your DNS hosting provider to enable DNSSEC signing.
top_fixes.title: Enable DNSSEC

top_fixes.fix: Publish a BIMI DNS record pointing to your brand logo (SVG Tiny PS format). For full support in Gmail, you will also need a Verified Mark Certificate (VMC).
top_fixes.title: Configure BIMI brand logo
